		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Isn't domino referring to a certain kind of tile game though? I have never heard of, for example, mahjong tiles being referred to as dominoes.<br />I think a generic term like &quot;tiles&quot; or &quot;panels&quot; would work.<br /><br />If it's a mini-game for your squirrel game, a squirrel theme is definitely the best, and you may actually not need any other theme or a story.<br /><br />If it's a stand-alone game, a story or selectable themes won't hurt IMHO.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
